Use the Properties menu button to display \
the workspace Properties submenu.   \
Use the Properties submenu to access global workspace properties windows.  \
Each window button on the Properties submenu brings up a property window \
for the following properties:

Programs Submenu

Icons

Color

Mouse Modifiers

Mouse Settings

Keyboard Settings

Miscellaneous

To display a property window, \
drag MENU onto the right half of the Properties menu button.  \
To choose a button from the Properties submenu, \
drag MENU onto a button on the submenu and release MENU.
